Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.06,1:38:44.94,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)}所以我学会了习惯
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.32,1:38:54.96,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)}Just me, just me, just me, just me
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.31,1:38:54.96,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)}孤独 孤独 孤独 孤独
