Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.28,1:39:09.32,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)}在学校里 我喜欢一个人吃饭
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.58,1:39:17.88,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)}Anyway, so I'll just stay
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.58,1:39:17.88,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)}无论如何 我都会待在
